           SPELL=grlogwipe
         VERSION=1.0
          SOURCE=$SPELL.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$SPELL
   SOURCE_URL[0]=http://grsecurity.net/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://www.grsecurity.net/misc.htm
         ENTERED=20020219
         UPDATED=20020219
           SHORT="grlogwipe is a full-featured syslog/wtmp/utmp/lastlog cleaner"
cat << EOF
Part of grsecurity utils.
grlogwipe is a full-featured log "cleaner" written from scratch.
it operates on both syslog logs as well as utmp/wtmp/lastlog entries.  It
also runs on multiple platforms (tested on freebsd 4.2 and linux) run
./grlogwipe -h for more information, including a description of each of
the options.
EOF
